Description: A comprehensive toolkit for morphometric shape analysis, including 
    Elliptical Fourier Analysis (EFA), Principal Component Analysis (PCA), 
    convex hull analysis, and advanced visualization tools for biological 
    shape data. The package provides functions for shape preprocessing, 
    statistical analysis, and publication-ready plotting capabilities.
